<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ḥbyby fty̱ mtẖl ạ̉rz lbnạn .. ḥbyby sqạh ʿmwdạ rkẖạm
 bdyʿ ạljmạl wḥlw ạllsạn .. wḥlqh ḥlạwẗ wklh ḥnạn
 ạlqrạr- (hw wḥdh ḥbyby .. gẖạfr jmyʿ zlạty)2
 (bh ạ̉ḥyạ wạ̉tḥrk wạ̉wjd .. hw sr ḥyạty)2
 2- dh ạ̉byḍ wạ̉ḥmr jmạlh ʿjyb .. wẓạhr fy jsmh jrwḥ ạlṣlyb
 mkẖlṣ wfạdy wrạʿy ạ̉myn .. ḥbyb wlạ ywjd mtẖlh ḥbyb
 3- nrạh byzrf dmwʿ ạlḥnạn .. lạ̉jl lʿạzr wyʿṭf ʿlyh
 wyʿṭy lmrym wmrtẖạ ạlạ̉mạn .. wyạ̉mr ftrjʿ ḥyạth ạ̹lyh
 4- whw ạlly ygẖfr jmyʿ ạldẖnwb .. wlys bạ̉ḥdiⁿ gẖyrh ạlkẖlạṣ
 whw ạlṭryq ạlwḥyd llsmạ .. whw ạlwsyṭ byn ạllh wạlnạs</lyrics>
<title>ḥbyby fty̱</title>
</song>